parameters:
MasamuneThis one is different from the other
dragons!

AmeliaI feel an incredible amount of magical
power. It's like she's been enhanced with some
kind of magic...
MasamuneCan it speak? Does it have intelligence?

Fierce Dragon, Dark TypeI am capable of being
tamed. The flames that burn within me are fierce
and unyielding.

MasamuneIf we extinguish the flames in the
cave... will the enhancement magic disappear?

MasamuneTo willingly reveal your weakness, it
seems you truly lack intelligence.
Fierce Dragon, Dark TypeI will devour you!

[Masamune] Let's search for the strengthened
flames.
Fierce Dragon, Dark TypeDon't underestimate me!
MasamuneYou seem much weaker than earlier.

I can't believe there are monsters like this, it
doesn't feel like a trial.
It feels like they're trying to kill us for real.
I can't defeat monsters like this.

I've never fought before, but demons are probably
much stronger.

Ahaha, I never expected that Masamune-kun would
come to my rescue...
When did you become so strong?

Honestly, it might be tough for Blanchette to
continue fighting.

The further the enemy goes inside, the stronger
they become.
You're holding us back, aren't you?
(It's as if she's been cursed in various ways...)
You think the same, Masamune-kun, don't you?
No... I'm just not feeling well today.
I know Amelia's strength the best.
When I'm not feeling well, I'll support you.
There's no problem with that, right?
If Amelia is fine with it...

(Actually, it would be better for Amelia to wait.
But I don't know what she'll do if I take my eyes
off her.)

Another door. I wonder what kind of mechanism it
has this time.
There's something written here this time.
Um, let's make this door glow...
Magic to make it glow... I can't use it.
Sure, I'll illuminate it right away.
Nothing is happening. What kind of magic is this?

It's a magic that shines light on a spherical
mirror and spins it. It's sparkling and beautiful,
isn't it?

Because it was recently developed to liven up the
drinking party.
That flashy magic won't open it!

Because it's an old facility, I don't think new
magic will work.

Looks like we have no choice but to search in the
library again.

Just a hunch, but I think we can find the magic
answer.

(Even though I'm in a hurry, it feels like I'm
being delayed...)

MasamuneIt won't open. We have to attend
Professor Jigoku's class and search for magic in
the library.
Registered on the dungeon teleportation stone.
MasamuneShall we call it a day?
I'll call it a day and return to my room
